.TH CATNIP-LSP 1 "March 2026" "catnip-tools" "Catnip Language"
.SH NAME
catnip-lsp \- Language Server Protocol server for Catnip
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B catnip-lsp
.RB [ \-\-stdio ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B catnip-lsp
is an LSP server for the Catnip language, built with tower-lsp in Rust.
It provides diagnostics, formatting, and rename support to editors that
speak the Language Server Protocol.
.PP
The server communicates over stdio by default and can be launched by editors
automatically or via
.B catnip lsp\fR.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B \-\-stdio
Use stdio for communication (default).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR catnip (1),
.BR catnip-repl (1)
